As WASPINATOR flew around and BLACKARACHNIA flitted through the trees
they could feel the tremors of the massive cave in that was finishing
beneath the ground. The trmors were just subsiding as energy began to
flicker, as if a doorway made of energy was opening and three figures
stepped through all of them of a dinosaur styled motif.

"Where is your master?" The lead one said looking around and spying
WASPINATOR. "Where is Hydras?"

(TAG)

- Preston
